name: Methamphetamine
description:
Thirteen-month-old Makavelii Leoni died from methamphetamine toxicity with 43 injuries to his body, including bruising and bite marks to his arm.
collage painting 3000*3000 pixel
His mother, Lina Marie Daley, pleaded guilty to manslaughter, drug trafficking, and 20 other summary offences in the Supreme Court in Cairns.
